text: public void UpdateItemResult(IInspectionItemResult itemResult) ] if(itemResult is null) { SelectedCompoDrawInfo = new List<DrawBaseInfo>(); SelectedCompProperties = new List<DictionaryEntry>(); SelectedResults = new List<DictionaryEntry>(); this.WhiteImageSource = null; this.UVImageSource = null; this.GeometryData = null; } else UpdateItemResultAsync(itemResult); }
